                </nav>

                <div class="container-fluid">
                    <h3 class="mt-4">Welcome to FSE-ESN</h2>
                    <p>
                        This is an Emergency Social Network. The goal is 
                        to provide you with a social network that you can use 
                        during emergency situations. 
                    </p>

                    <p><span><img src="/assets/ok.png" class="rounded-circle mr-1" width="30" height="30"></span>   OK - I am OK. I do not need help.</p>
                    <p><span><img src="/assets/help.png" class="rounded-circle mr-1" width="30" height="30"></span>   HELP - I need help, but this is not a life threatening emergency.</p>
                    <p><span><img src="/assets/emergency.png" class="rounded-circle mr-1" width="30" height="30"></span>   EMERGENCY - I need help now. This is a life threatening emergency.</p>
                    <form action="/chatroom">
                        <button type="submit" class="btnSubmit">Agree</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
